songs.title: L0$3R
songs.lyrics:
Do not you realize how pathetic you are?
You have to refuse to accept yourself as you are

Everybody looks at you like you're crap, you're crap, you're crap
No matter how many times you repeat it, it will always be the same
No matter how many times I ignore it, they will continue there

Dear society, Fuck you

Are you there? Could you look at me without judging me?
Fuck you, fuck society
And between the society I am, that fuck sadboytaki
